(1, 1, 'Un comentarista de WordPress', 'wapuu@wordpress.example', 'https://wordpress.org/', '', '2019-11-21 00:13:08', '2019-11-20 23:13:08', 'Hola, esto es un comentario.\nPara empezar a moderar, editar y borrar comentarios, por favor, visita la pantalla de comentarios en el escritorio.\nLos avatares de los comentaristas provienen de <a href=\"https://gravatar.com\">Gravatar</a>.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(2, 251, 'A WordPress Commenter', 'wapuu@wordpress.example', 'https://wordpress.org/', '', '2019-01-08 04:30:03', '2019-01-08 04:30:03', 'Hi, this is a comment.\nTo get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard.\nCommenter avatars come from <a href=\\\"https://gravatar.com\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow ugc\\\">Gravatar</a>.', 0, 'trash', '', '', 0, 0),
(3, 25, 'Zahid Smith', 'softhopperbd@gmail.com', 'https://softhopper.net', '116.58.203.31', '2019-01-08 07:02:56', '2019-01-08 07:02:56', 'The island of saints and scholars is as redundant a phrase as any other Irish cliche we choose to perpetuate', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(4, 25, 'Zahid Smith', 'softhopperbd@gmail.com', 'https://softhopper.net', '116.58.203.31', '2019-01-08 07:03:13', '2019-01-08 07:03:13', 'Programming is still in its infancy. In fact, two of the very first programming languages ever invented are still being used today', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(5, 25, 'Zahid Smith', 'softhopperbd@gmail.com', 'https://softhopper.net', '116.58.203.31', '2019-01-08 07:03:44', '2019-01-08 07:03:44', 'All major tech companies, from Google to Facebook, aggressively compete to hire gifted young coders. In the Silicon Valley area', 0, '1', '', '', 3, 0),
(6, 25, 'Zahid Smith', 'softhopperbd@gmail.com', 'https://softhopper.net', '116.58.203.31', '2019-01-08 07:03:58', '2019-01-08 07:03:58', 'Even so, this shows us programming has barely started on its own evolutionary path.', 0, 'trash', '', '', 5, 0);
